    "description": "Duos Technologies Group, Inc., develops and deploys technology systems with a focus on inspecting and evaluating moving vehicles. The Company operates under its brand name duostech. Its technology focus is within the Vision Technology market sector and, more specifically, the Machine Vision subsector. Machine Vision companies provide imaging-based automatic inspection and analysis for process control for industry with potential expansion into other markets. The Company s flagship product, the Railcar Inspection Portal (RIP), enables freight and transit railroad customers and selects government agencies to conduct fully automated railcar inspections in real-time as trains move at full speed. It has also developed the Automated Logistics Information System (ALIS) which can automate gatehouse operations where transport trucks enter and exit large logistics and intermodal facilities. Its subsidiaries include Duos Technologies, Inc., Duos Edge AI, Inc., and Duos Energy Corporation.",
